00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:03.790
To register for classes,
you'll use a system called OSCAR.

00:00:03.790 --> 00:00:07.520
OSCAR stands for Online Student
Computer-Assisted Registration.

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:11.838
To access OSCAR, go to oscar.gatech.edu.

00:00:11.838 --> 00:00:14.118
You can also access it through BuzzPort,
but

00:00:14.118 --> 00:00:17.140
it's easier just to
go straight to OSCAR.

00:00:17.140 --> 00:00:20.150
Then, click Secured Access Login.

00:00:20.150 --> 00:00:22.850
Now log in using your nine-digit ID.

00:00:22.850 --> 00:00:25.240
And use your six-digit PIN number.

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:28.330
The first time you log in,
your PIN with be your birthdate.

00:00:28.330 --> 00:00:29.940
You'll then be asked to change it.

00:00:29.940 --> 00:00:33.610
If you forget your PIN,
you can click Forgot PIN below.

00:00:33.610 --> 00:00:35.940
After you log in, you'll be in OSCAR.

00:00:35.940 --> 00:00:38.030
Now, we'll talk about
how to find classes.

